column5: Hey Cliff!!  Glad you found it.  It's been a while since I recorded that song!!
Me too Cliff, 2008 I believe. Still love it! Was looking around on YouTube last night and found some other stuff you had done. Brought back some good memories
Always dug that Video / Board Anthem-haven't heard it in years-looked like 10 feet of work for the dude that did it Have a wicked weekend All  Think Rain-man these gardens are dry Paul.
